ess. The particular veggies that your recipes require isn't your only consideration... you can only take a limited number of pips with each chop, and the right dice values can unlock all sorts of drool-worthy Hypes to boost a recipe's score!</p>\n\n<p>A clever cleaver is all you need to whip up delicious recipes in this dice-slicing game for up to four chefs!</p>\n\n<p><em>&mdash;description from the publisher</em></p>\n\n","wiki":"<span class='text-muted'>This page does not exist. You can edit this page to create it.</span>","website":{"url":"https://www.kidstablebg.com/dicedveggies","title":"Diced Veggies - Official KTBG website"},"imageid":"7373886","images":{"thumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/WYW6fkRj6BEazZ75TYcsHA__small/img/RnMRcxnQoZoXF50lyQoI7NJCbPA=/fit-in/200x150/filters:strip_icc()/pic7373886.jpg","micro":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/WYW6fkRj6BEazZ75TYcsHA__micro/img/48O2nK416C7VbSand0fq6Dnt-nY=/fit-in/64x64/filters:strip_icc()/pic7373886.jpg","square":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/WYW6fkRj6BEazZ75TYcsHA__square/img/n5ShZqLJRWk-II0s8RBaCP_JV3M=/75x75/filters:strip_icc()/pic7373886.jpg","tallthumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/WYW6fkRj6BEazZ75TYcsHA__tallthumb/img/7f2ggzNjwWEZxYneTEsCtIKToZE=/fit-in/75x125/filters:strip_icc()/pic7373886.jpg","previewthumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/WYW6fkRj6BEazZ75TYcsHA__previewthumb/img/15ePRnIB2y9f4h8FVO07PVDM0L4=/fit-in/300x320/filters:strip_icc()/pic7373886.jpg","square200":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/WYW6fkRj6BEazZ75TYcsHA__square200/img/jI_FEvcaRveBAhlz980CdGAxess=/200x200/filters:strip_icc()/pic7373886.jpg","original":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/WYW6fkRj6BEazZ75TYcsHA__original/img/E9SD1YnRjc8dpL1A5xspeXpZpHY=/0x0/filters:format(jpeg)/pic7373886.jpg"},"imagepagehref":"/image/7373886/diced-veggies","imageurl":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/WYW6fkRj6BEazZ75TYcsHA__itemrep/img/dB7qEDo6X11INGwbKOiAG7MVYiA=/fit-in/246x300/filters:strip_icc()/pic7373886.jpg","imageurl@2x":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/WYW6fkR